room_title: Escape room "Wanted in the West" by Brainy Actz in Temecula
room_address: 28481 Rancho California Rd. Suite #108, Temecula, CA 92590
room_description: You and your gang of outlaws have recently been making a name for yourselves.  Some people say if you’re not stopped, you might end up being the most notorious gang the West has ever seen.  However, you’ve recently pushed your luck, and one of your most trusted members has sold you out to a local town sheriff.  He’s taken your gold and has you locked up, while you wait for trial in the mornin’.  Is this the end of the road for ya, or you gone saddle up, and take back what’s yours…
